<Base title="SocialProof for Moving Companies — Reviews That Win More Moves | SocialProof" description="Moving companies: stand out in a crowded market with authentic customer testimonials. SocialProof helps you collect and display reviews that convert quote requests into booked moves.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Moving Companies
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Moving is stressful. Customers are handing strangers access to everything they own. Before they book, they need to know: are these movers careful? Are they honest? Do they show up on time? The answer comes from other customers — and SocialProof makes sure those stories are front and center on your website.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Trust is everything in moving</h2>
      <p>A customer comparing moving companies isn't just comparing prices. They're asking: "Can I trust these people with my grandmother's china, my kids' beds, and everything I own?" Reviews from real customers who came through their move safely are your most powerful sales tool.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Moving company horror stories are everywhere online. A wall of positive testimonials from verified customers immediately separates you from the fly-by-night operations charging less and delivering damage.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The testimonials that book more moves</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Care and handling:</strong> "Not a single item was damaged. The crew wrapped everything carefully and took their time."</li>
        <li><strong>Professionalism:</strong> "Showed up exactly on time with the right crew size. No excuses, no upsells, just the job done."</li>
        <li><strong>Pricing transparency:</strong> "Quoted $X and charged $X. No surprise fees at the end."</li>
        <li><strong>Efficiency:</strong> "Moved our 3-bedroom house in 5 hours. Efficient and organized."</li>
        <li><strong>Long-distance trust:</strong> "Moved from Texas to Oregon and everything arrived intact and on schedule. Unbelievable service."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for movers</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your quote page, services page, or homepage.</li>
        <li><strong>After each move</strong>, send the feedback link via text or email. Customers respond in under 2 minutes.</li>
        <li><strong>Approve and publish</strong> in one click — testimonials appear on your site instantly.</li>
        <li><strong>Segment by service</strong> — local moves, long-distance, office relocations, specialty items.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for every type of moving service</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Local residential moves</li>
        <li>Long-distance and interstate moves</li>
        <li>Corporate and office relocations</li>
        <li>Apartment and dorm moves</li>
        <li>Senior and assisted-living transitions</li>
        <li>Specialty moves (pianos, art, antiques)</li>
        <li>Storage and full-service packing</li>
      </ul>

      <div style="background:#fff7ed;border:1px solid #fed7aa;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem;margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <p style="font-size:1.1rem;font-style:italic;color:#9a3412;">
          "We were losing quote requests to companies with more reviews. After three months using SocialProof, we had 40+ testimonials on our site and our booking rate doubled. The reviews do the selling."
        </p>
        <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#c2410c;margin-top:0.5rem;">— James K., owner, K&T Moving, Nashville</p>
      </div>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
      <p>Add a testimonial widget to your site in minutes. No developer required. Free forever for 1 active widget — no credit card needed to start.</p>
      <div style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" style="background:#f97316;color:#fff;padding:0.9rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;">
          Start Free — No Credit Card Required
        </a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:2rem;color:#777;font-size:0.9rem;">
        Also useful for: <a href="/for/contractors" style="color:#f97316;">contractors</a>, <a href="/for/handymen" style="color:#f97316;">handymen</a>, <a href="/for/pressure-washing" style="color:#f97316;">pressure washing</a>, <a href="/for/local-service" style="color:#f97316;">local service businesses</a>
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>

